# Spider Log API
Provides service for Spider Log app family, recording world's spider sightings.

# Group Spiders
Access to Spyder resources

## My Spiders [/spiders]
### Get all my spider sightings [GET]
+ Request
    + Headers
    
            Authorization: Basic ABCDEF
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)

