## My Spiders [/spiders{?page,size}]        
### Get page with my spider sightings [GET]
+ Parameters
    + page:1 (number, required) - page number
    + size:10 (number, required) - page size

+ Request
    + Headers
    
            Authorization: Basic ABCDEF
            x-api-version: 1.0
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "pages":
